# External reference source trees.
#
# These directories are read-only design references, not project source,
# dependencies, docs, tests, or build inputs. Ordinary rg / audit searches
# should skip them unless a task explicitly asks to inspect external references.
docs/external-references/**

# Keep the normalized target names explicit so future directory renames remain
# isolated even if the parent rule is narrowed later.
docs/external-references/claude-code/**
docs/external-references/deepseek/**
docs/external-references/cc-switch/**

